properties.Name: IdentificationType
properties.Description:
A type of identification.

Ex:
- Company Issued
- Passport
- VISA
- Drivers License
- Social Security Number (SSN)
- Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN)
- Country Tax Number
- State Tax Number
- National Tax Number
- Country Corporation Number
- Medicare Health Insurance Card Number
- Medicaid ID Number
- Military ID Number
- Known Traveler / PASS ID
- Redress Number
- Employer Identification Number (EIN)
